The hotel itself was clean and comfortable - we had a room with a balcony and the bathroom was modern and well equipped.	Breakfast was good and the public rooms including the breakfast room are very nicely done, modern and clean.	The room itself was a bit small, but typical of Europe...the bathroom and shower were good, so no complaints about room or noise.	The rooms were decent, though small in size, and the shower was great with a rain shower option.	The room was clean and reasonably quiet, and the view from the window was at air conditioning units and walls.